<TEXT>
<P>
Millions of Iranians chanting "Death to America!" and beating themselves in 
ritualistic grief surrounded the gold-domed tomb of the Ayatollah Ruhollah 
Khomeini, ending days of mourning for the founder of the Islamic republic. 
Speeches by his religious successor, President Ali Khamenei, who appeared in 
