York's Little Italy section, setting the neighborhood abuzz as fans try to 
catch a glimpse of the superstar actor. A crew member told Reuters that the new 
movie is a "Mafia comedy," but Brando's publicists won't go that far. "Brando 
plays a distributor. Matthew Broderick plays a film student. That's all I can 
say," says Debbie Nathan, a spokeswoman for the production. ALEENE MacMINN 
